      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle, then take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing it with the side of a knife and discard the skin</p><p>Chop your <strong>ginger</strong> in half</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
