    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>and your <strong>diced chicken breast </strong>to the dish with your <strong>Thai green curry paste </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
